results.title: A+X (2012) #1
results.description: - Spinning directly out of AVX! - Like AVX: VS., this book brings you two stories every month by the industry's top creators! - This issue features a Wolverine/Hulk story by Jeph Loeb (WOLVERINE) and Hulk-legend Dale Keown and a Captain America/Cable story by Dan Slott (AMAZING SPIDER-MAN) and Ron Garney (WOLVERINE)!

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #2
results.description: Professor X's five original students have been flung from the past to present day. While they cope with an unimaginable future (especially considering the fallout of AVX), how will today's X-Men justify their actions to their past selves?

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #3
results.description: - The flagship X-Book marches on! - The original 5 X-Men are back, but that's not all that's happening. - What happened to the Phoenix 5 from AVENGERS VS. X-MEN?

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #4
results.description: - The Original 5 X-Men come face to face with their counterparts...and it isn't a peaceful meeting!

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #5
results.description: The first story of a new era comes to its conclusion.One of the original X-Men will be forever changed!

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #7
results.description: Mystique targets our young time-travelers, starting with Cyclops.

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #8
results.description: Guest-starring the Avengers!How will the Earth’s Mightiest Heroes react to the time-swept X-Men?

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #9
results.description: The Original Five X-Men get new costumes!Series main-artist Stuart Immonen returns!Mystique makes her big move.

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #10
results.description: The Uncanny X-Men come to the Jean Grey School to recruit.  Who will join Cyclops and his revolutionary crew? The answer will shock you!  And Mystique and Sabretooth continue to hatch their master plan and it doesn’t bode well for the All-New X-Men.

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #11
results.description: One of the ALL-NEW X-MEN leaves to join Cyclops and his crew! Jean Grey pushes her power to the limit, shaking her and the rest of the X-Men to the core.

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #12
results.description: The All-New X-Men find themselves face-to-face with the UNCANNY AVENGERS! Young Cyclops meets the adult version of the little brother he thought he may never see again.

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #13
results.description: The All-New X-Men are confronted by the Uncanny Avengers.  How does Havok deal with a teenaged version of his older brother Cyclops?

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #14
results.description: Jean Grey vs. Mastermind!  Years ago, one run in with this famous Brotherhood of Evil Mutants member was the beginning of the end of Jean Grey.  Will history repeat itself?

results.title: All-New X-Men (2012) #15
results.description: Love is in the air! Cyclops’ heart and future start to fade before his eyes as Jean Grey begins to slip away.

results.title: A+X (2012) #2
results.description: It's a teamup of two of the biggest Marvel movie ladies -- Black Widow and Rogue versus Sentinels!  Plus, Iron Man, Kitty Pryde, and Lockheed battle the Brood!

results.title: A+X (2012) #3
results.description: Storm and Black Panther's first post-AVX encounter! Avengers vs X-Men torn their union asunder, but can they put their past aside to take down a major threat in the present?  Plus, Gambit and Hawkeye team up!

results.title: A+X (2012) #4
results.description: Spider-Man and Beast fight zombies while Captain America teams up with his unlikliest ally yet - Kid Omega Quentin Quire!
